    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "The listener module handles the processing of incoming requests from Slack. Listeners:"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "\u2023 Match incoming requests against predefined conditions\n\u2023 Acknowledge requests from Slack\n\u2023 Process request data\n\u2023 Send responses back to Slack"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "The module provides both *synchronous* (thread-based) and *asynchronous* (asyncio-based) implementations, with separate runners, error handlers, and lifecycle hooks for each execution model."
      }
    }
